metadata.description: Before he was code-named Duke and was brought into the G.I. Joes, he was the top kick of a special ops team. Learn the legacy of Clan Destro in a bloody history lesson you'll never forget. Using her feminine wiles and deadly styles, the Baroness plans to steal a centuries-old valuable from a billionaire oil sheik. Find out what Snake Eyes was up to before the events of the movie, G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra!
metadata.name: G.I. Joe: Movie Prequel
